item.title: SoftLayer_Ticket_Subject
item.description: SoftLayer_Ticket_Subject Service Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Ticket_Subject data type models one of the possible subjects that a standard support ticket may belong to. A basic support ticket’s title matches it’s corresponding subject’s name. Local categoryId The subject category id that this ticket subject belongs to. Type: integer id A ticket subject's internal identifier. Type: integer name A ticket subject's name.
